### How it works now
```
Make.com runs every 6 hours
    ↓
Claude assesses a new tool → clean JSON
    ↓
HTTP 11 writes it to pending.json (zero manipulation)
    ↓
GitHub detects pending.json changed
    ↓
merge-tool.yml runs Python script
    ↓
Python reads pending.json + tools.json properly
    ↓
Prepends new tool, checks for duplicates, writes back
    ↓
AI Disco updates automatically
